=== sw-cor24-rpg-ii Minimal RPG-II Demo (Reverse-Field Variant) ===
Program:
H  control header
F  input file INFIL
I  field 01: A0110  (10-char input slice)
I  field 02: A0810  (3-char input tail slice)
C  REVR02 -> calc work field
O  DETAIL01 output (10 chars)
O  DETAIL02 output (3 chars)

Current boundary:
- Real today: the tiny parsed C-spec subset now includes one second behavior,
  REVR, which reverses the selected decoded input field before output.
- Placeholder today: calc parsing is still one-op-at-a-time, with no general
  expression engine or chained C-spec execution.

Current runtime-produced output:
A10
B20
C30

